title: Exception throws when exporting data from table containing highlight/map.
description: Exception throws when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When trying to export the data from a table which contains a highlight or map, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting the data from the table, the export should be successful and no exception should be thrown.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Locate a table that contains a highlight or map.
3. Try to export the data from the table.
4. Verify that the export is successful and no exception is thrown.
